install:
        mutt [MUA, Message User Agent], 
        w3m [text based browser for viewing html type mail in mutt],
        offlineimap [MRA, Message Retrieval Agent], 
        msmtp [MTA, Message Transfer Agent]

        procmail & fetchmail isn't used

and place their configuration files in $HOME


add idlemail.py as utility to start offlineimap process when there are new messages to be synced on the server. run idlemail.py as a daemon.
